HEADWORD: nonremittal
<hw>nonremittal</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of failing
to meet a financial obligation.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> default, nonpayment.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A loss resulting from failure of a debt to be
paid.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nonpayment, default.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

